Interface IMolecularFormulaSet

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, ICDKObject

AdductFormula, AdductFormula, DebugAdductFormula, DebugMolecularFormulaSet, MolecularFormulaSet, MolecularFormulaSet, NNAdductFormula, NNMolecularFormulaSet
public interface IMolecularFormulaSet
extends ICDKObject

Class defining a molecular formula object. It maintains a list of list IMoleculaFormula.

Examples:

  • [C5H5]-
  • C6H6
  • 12C513CH6
